Speech_R_Today: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE()) SET @Node = @NODE   select cast(round((100 * ((sum(pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeech) - sum(pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeechCnInit)) / (sum(pmNoNormalRabReleaseSpeech) + sum(pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeech)))),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS LatestMeasureValue from  (select RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID,pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeech,pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeechCnInit,pmNoNormalRabReleaseSpeech from DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW where   UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@date AND RNC  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED')) a where RNC like @Node group by RNC
Speech_R_PastWeek: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE()) SET @Node = @NODE select cast(round((100 * ((sum(pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeech) - sum(pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeechCnInit)) / (sum(pmNoNormalRabReleaseSpeech) + sum(pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeech)))),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS LatestMeasureValue from (select RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID,pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeech,pmNoSystemRabReleaseSpeechCnInit,pmNoNormalRabReleaseSpeech from DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW where  UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@dateprev AND UTC_DATETIME_ID<@datelast AND RNC  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED')) a where RNC like @Node group by RNC
PacketintHs_R_Today: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE()) SET @Node = @NODE select  cast(round((100 *((sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConnData) + sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnDataToSpeech)) / (sum(pmNormalReleaseHsConn) + sum(pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) + sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConn) + sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) + sum(pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn)))),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS LatestMeasureValue from  ( select RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID,sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConn) as pmSystemReleaseHsConn ,sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech)  as pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech,sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConnCnInit) as pmSystemReleaseHsConnCnInit,sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeechCnInit) as   pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeechCnInit ,sum(pmNormalReleaseHsConn) as pmNormalReleaseHsConn,sum(pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) as pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech,  sum(pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn) as pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn,sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConnData) as pmSystemReleaseHsConnData,sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnDataToSpeech) as pmSystemRelMultiHsConnDataToSpeech from DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW where  UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@date AND RNC LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID) a where RNC like @Node group by RNC
PacketintHs_R_PastWeek: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE())SET @Node = @NODE select  cast(round((100 *((sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConnData) + sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnDataToSpeech)) / (sum(pmNormalReleaseHsConn) + sum(pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) + sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConn) + sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) + sum(pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn)))),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS LatestMeasureValue from (select RNC, UTC_DATETIME_ID, sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConn) as pmSystemReleaseHsConn, sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) as pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech,sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConnCnInit) as pmSystemReleaseHsConnCnInit,sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeechCnInit) as pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeechCnInit, sum(pmNormalReleaseHsConn) as pmNormalReleaseHsConn,sum(pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) as pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech, sum(pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn) as pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn,sum(pmSystemReleaseHsConnData) as pmSystemReleaseHsConnData,sum(pmSystemRelMultiHsConnDataToSpeech) as pmSystemRelMultiHsConnDataToSpeech from DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW where  UTC_DATETIME_ID >=@dateprev AND UTC_DATETIME_ID <@datelast AND RNC  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID) a where RNC like @Node group by RNC
PacketintHs_IDl_Tp_Today: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode  SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE()) SET @Node = @NODE  select  cast(round((sum(pmSumAckedBitsRlim) / (0.002 *sum (pmSumTransmissionsRlim))),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS LatestMeasureValue  from (  SELECT  sum( D1. pmSumAckedBitsRlim ) AS  PMSUMACKEDBITSRLIM, sum(D1. pmSumTransmissionsRlim ) AS PMSUMTRANSMISSIONSRLIM, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID, D1.RBS AS RBS FROM DC_E_RBS_HSDSCHRES_V_RAW D1 WHERE (UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@date) AND D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') and RBS like @Node GROUP BY  D1.RBS, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID)a where RBS like @Node group by RBS
PacketintHs_IDl_Tp_PastWeek: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE()) SET @Node = @NODE  select  cast(round((sum(pmSumAckedBitsRlim) / (0.002 *sum (pmSumTransmissionsRlim))),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS LatestMeasureValue  from (  SELECT  sum( D1. pmSumAckedBitsRlim ) AS  PMSUMACKEDBITSRLIM, sum(D1. pmSumTransmissionsRlim ) AS PMSUMTRANSMISSIONSRLIM, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID, D1.RBS AS RBS FROM DC_E_RBS_HSDSCHRES_V_RAW D1 WHERE (UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@dateprev AND UTC_DATETIME_ID<@datelast) AND D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED') and RBS like @Node GROUP BY  D1.RBS, D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID)a where RBS like @Node group by RBS

PacketintHs_U_MHT_Today: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode  SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @Node = @NODE         SELECT cast(round(900 * max(D1.final_pm_count) *((sum([pmSumHsConnServ]) / sum([pmSamplesHsConnServ])) / (sum([pmNormalReleaseHsConn]) + sum([pmSystemReleaseHsConn]) + sum([pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech]) + sum([pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech]) + sum([pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn]))),2) as numeric(36,6)) as [LatestMeasureValue] FROM (select max(PM_COUNT) as final_pm_count from (SELECT COUNT(*) AS PM_COUNT FROM DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW D1 WHERE DATE_ID=@date AND SN  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by UTC_DATETIME_ID)D)D1 , (    SELECT    SUM(D1.pmSumHsConnServ) AS pmSumHsConnServ,    SUM(D1.pmSamplesHsConnServ) AS pmSamplesHsConnServ,    SUM(D1.pmNormalReleaseHsConn) AS pmNormalReleaseHsConn,    SUM(D1.pmSystemReleaseHsConn) AS pmSystemReleaseHsConn,    SUM(D1.pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) AS pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech,    SUM(D1.pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) AS pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech,    SUM(D1.pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn) AS pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn,    D1.SN AS SN,    D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM    DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW D1 WHERE     UTC_DATETIME_ID >= @date and SN like @node AND     D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')  GROUP BY D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID,SN)D2
PacketintHs_U_MHT_PastWeek: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @Node = @NODE   SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE())    SELECT cast(round(900 * max(D1.final_pm_count) *((sum([pmSumHsConnServ]) / sum([pmSamplesHsConnServ])) / (sum([pmNormalReleaseHsConn]) + sum([pmSystemReleaseHsConn]) + sum([pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech]) + sum([pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech]) + sum([pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn]))),2) as numeric(36,6)) as [LatestMeasureValue] FROM (select max(PM_COUNT) as final_pm_count from (SELECT COUNT(*) AS PM_COUNT FROM DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW D1 WHERE DATE_ID=@date AND SN  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by UTC_DATETIME_ID)D)D1, (      SELECT    SUM(D1.pmSumHsConnServ) AS pmSumHsConnServ,    SUM(D1.pmSamplesHsConnServ) AS pmSamplesHsConnServ,    SUM(D1.pmNormalReleaseHsConn) AS pmNormalReleaseHsConn,    SUM(D1.pmSystemReleaseHsConn) AS pmSystemReleaseHsConn,    SUM(D1.pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) AS pmNormalRelMultiHsConnToSpeech,    SUM(D1.pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech) AS pmSystemRelMultiHsConnToSpeech,    SUM(D1.pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn) AS pmReconfSuccOrigHsConn,    D1.SN AS SN,    D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID AS UTCDATETIMEID FROM    DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW D1 WHERE     UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@dateprev AND UTC_DATETIME_ID <@datelast and SN like @node AND     D1.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE','SUSPECTED')  GROUP BY D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID,SN)D2
Packetint_U_Trafficvolume_Today: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE,@NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE()) SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE())  SET @Node = @NODE        SELECT cast(round((sum(D1.[pmSumDchDlRlcTotPacketThp])/2 + sum(D2.[pmSumHsDlRlcUserPacketThp])/10 + sum(D1.[pmSumDchUlRlcTotPacketThp])/2 + sum(D3.[pmSumEulRlcUserPacketThp])/10),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS  LatestMeasureValue FROM      ( SELECT RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID,sum(pmSumDchDlRlcTotPacketThp) as pmSumDchDlRlcTotPacketThp, sum(pmSumDchUlRlcTotPacketThp) as pmSumDchUlRlcTotPacketThp FROM DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW WHERE UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@date AND RNC  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID )D1  ,      ( SELECT RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID,sum(pmSumHsDlRlcUserPacketThp) as pmSumHsDlRlcUserPacketThp FROM DC_E_RAN_HSDSCH_RAW WHERE UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@date AND RNC  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID)D2 ,  ( SELECT RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID,sum(pmSumEulRlcUserPacketThp) as pmSumEulRlcUserPacketThp  FROM DC_E_RAN_EUL_RAW WHERE UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@date AND RNC  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by RNC,UTC_DATETIME_ID)D3  WHERE D1.RNC=D2.RNC AND D2.RNC=D3.RNC AND D1.RNC LIke @Node and D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID=D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID and D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID=D3.UTC_DATETIME_ID GROUP BY D1.RNC
Packetint_U_Trafficvolume_Pastweek: DECLARE @date DATE,@dateprev DATE,@datelast DATE, @NODE varchar(50) = @uiNode SET @date = @uiDate SET @dateprev = DATEADD(dd, -7, GETDATE())       SET @Node = @NODE  SET @datelast = DATEADD(dd, -6, GETDATE())      SELECT cast(round((sum(D1.[pmSumDchDlRlcTotPacketThp])/2 + sum(D2.[pmSumHsDlRlcUserPacketThp])/10 + sum(D1.[pmSumDchUlRlcTotPacketThp])/2 + sum(D3.[pmSumEulRlcUserPacketThp])/10),2) as numeric(36,6)) AS  LatestMeasureValue FROM      ( SELECT SN,UTC_DATETIME_ID,sum(pmSumDchDlRlcTotPacketThp) as pmSumDchDlRlcTotPacketThp, sum(pmSumDchUlRlcTotPacketThp) as pmSumDchUlRlcTotPacketThp FROM DC_E_RAN_UCELL_RAW WHERE UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@dateprev AND UTC_DATETIME_ID <@datelast AND SN  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by SN,UTC_DATETIME_ID )D1  ,      ( SELECT SN,UTC_DATETIME_ID,sum(pmSumHsDlRlcUserPacketThp) as pmSumHsDlRlcUserPacketThp FROM DC_E_RAN_HSDSCH_RAW WHERE UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@dateprev AND UTC_DATETIME_ID <@datelast AND SN  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by SN,UTC_DATETIME_ID)D2 ,  ( SELECT SN,UTC_DATETIME_ID,sum(pmSumEulRlcUserPacketThp) as pmSumEulRlcUserPacketThp  FROM DC_E_RAN_EUL_RAW WHERE UTC_DATETIME_ID>=@dateprev AND UTC_DATETIME_ID <@datelast AND SN  LIKE '%rnc%' AND ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') group by SN,UTC_DATETIME_ID)D3  WHERE D1.SN=D2.SN AND D2.SN=D3.SN AND D1.SN LIke @Node and D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID=D2.UTC_DATETIME_ID and D1.UTC_DATETIME_ID=D3.UTC_DATETIME_ID GROUP BY D1.SN
